00:00:10.600 --> 00:00:12.600
or difficult situations.

00:00:13.180 --> 00:00:16.140
Your choice of words and the phrases that you use can

00:00:16.140 --> 00:00:19.660
affect what customers and your colleagues think of you.

00:00:19.700 --> 00:00:22.760
So, if you speak English as a second or a third language,

00:00:22.760 --> 00:00:25.680
using the right words in the right way

00:00:25.680 --> 00:00:26.960
is really important.

00:00:26.960 --> 00:00:29.360
I'm Emma from mmmEnglish

00:00:29.360 --> 00:00:32.840
